Heat oven to 425 degrees F. Mix Pasta, Sauce Mix and remaining ingredients except peanuts in ungreased 2-quart casserole or rectangular pan, 10x6x1 1/2 inches. Cover and bake 30 minutes or until pasta is tender; stir. Let stand uncovered 5 minutes or until sauce is as thick as you'd like. Sprinkle with peanuts if desired.